	   <tr><td colspan=2>Bah.&nbsp;&nbsp;JBBs will never be touched.  Want to know why?  It is useful for about 5 levels.  After that, the mobs have SO many frikin hit points, 263 isn't squat.  When a mob has 10K hp, and you are doing 263....  I bet it feels worse off when it gets a shaving nick in the morning.  Also, with Velious, the Cold resist of the average mob is going to be high enough to make it a novelty.<br><br>They already "fixed" the drop rate on it anyway.<br><br>Yes it is cool in the old world and Kunark.  Fighting 50+ mobs (like in Icewell Keep *shudder*  Quads for 220 on an EVEN con) in Velious and the Higher Kunark zones, where that 7 second casting time is a Gheal or Sheal that could have saved the enchanter......<br><br>JBB's are nice (like a manastone), but not all that.  Now, gimme the epic spear, with a huge free DoT, +20 wis, and resists.......<br><br>Gorthin Spiritcaller<br>51 Shaman Bristlebane<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
